nalytical slope and pole-density\nprofiles, but pile heights/contents need a t-dependent numerical search of up\nto two roots to get V(t). A summary, a discussion and hints of generalizations\nare provided, and open problems are evoked.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 16:48:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
