entional bilingual NMT, that the transformer NMT outperforms recurrent NMT,\nand that zero-shot NMT outperforms conventional pivoting methods and even\nmatches the performance of a fully-trained bilingual system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 17:22:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
