 by\nthe hot mode in halo masses well below the classic threshold of ~10^12 M_sun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 18:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 17:56:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 22:46:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
