 of\nconnections as well as identification of the fail-safe points for secure and\nfast operations. Furthermore, the evaluations help to follow the multiple\ntradeoffs of security and performance based on the metrics like mandatory key\nupdates, the range of operations and the probability of connectivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 03:17:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
