ompact subgroup\nof $\\text{G}(m)$ when $m>n$.\n  Given a continuous map $f:M \\rightarrow N$ between compact hyperbolic\nmanifolds, we also obtain an adaptation of the mapping degree theorem to this\ncontext.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 10:59:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 20:26:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
