 gain in\nsampling the folded states by at least 2.3x. Our study provides a quantitative\nbasis to understand how DL driven MD simulations, can lead to effective\nperformance gains and reduced times to solution on supercomputing resources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 13:58:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
